  "text": "In the present study, we aimed to investigate the impact of the K121Q SNP in the ENPP1 gene, which was reported to be associated with type 2 diabetes in a recent meta-analysis [CITATION_1] , on the success of a lifestyle intervention programme in individuals at increased risk of type 2 diabetes.",
